<xref id="IFRS17_X0999" base="F59422234" href="IFRS17_B97.dita#IFRS17_B97">paragraph&#xa0;B97(c)</xref>,                     the entity does not adjust the contractual service margin for the experience                     adjustment of CU50 defined as the difference between the estimate at the                     beginning of the period of insurance service expenses expected to be incurred in                     the period of CU200 and the actual insurance service expenses incurred in the                     period of CU150. Applying <xref id="IFRS17_X1000" base="F59422235" href="IFRS17_104.dita#IFRS17_104">paragraph&#xa0;104</xref>, the entity classifies                     those changes as related to current service.</p></li></ol>             </entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>